dialogue.text: Ok, what do you like to do?
Well I am a cook. Do you like any foods
I am good how are you?
Doing fine, just listening to some music.
What do you like to listen to?
Mostly rock music, my favorite band is Led Zeppelin
They have the song Stairway to Heaven right?
Yes it's my favorite, I highly recommend listening if you haven't!
I will, thanks for the recommendation!
